      <td style="text-align: left">False</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">Octet String<br />Derived using the SHA-1 hash of the Issuer’s public key in accordance with RFC 5280.  Must match SKI of issuing CA Certificate</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">Subject Key Identifier</td>
