    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">Certificate Policies</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">Mandatory</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">False</td>
      <td style="text-align: left"><strong>Required Certificate Policy Fields:</strong> <br />See Section 7.1.6.4. The certificate shall include all the certificate policy OIDs for all certificates issued by the CA and covered by the OCSP responses. <br /><br /><strong>Optional Certificate Policy Fields:</strong> <br /> certificatePolicies:policyQualifiers <br /> policyQualifierId   id-qt 1 <br /> qualifier:cPSuri</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">Authority Information Access</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">Optional</td>
