    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">nextUpdate</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">Encoded as UTCTime for dates through 2049 and GeneralizedTime for dates thereafter <br /> See Section 4.9.7 for validity period intervals.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">Revoked Certificates List</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">0 or more 2-tuple of certificate serial number and revocation date (Expressed in UTCTime for dates until end of 2049 and GeneralizedTime for dates thereafter)</td>
    </tr>
